      "title": "Block & Leviton LLP Announces Proposed Class Action Settlement on Behalf of Purchasers of Common Stock of Biogen, Inc. \u2013 BIIB",
      "summary": "A federal court has approved an $18.9 million settlement for investors who purchased Biogen Inc. common stock between June 8, 2021 and July 12, 2021. A settlement hearing is scheduled for September 29, 2026, to determine if the settlement is fair and reasonable. Class members must submit a Proof of Claim by September 24, 2026 to receive compensation.",
